-- Nikkei 225 January Options Settle at 8,470.71, Traders Say
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2012-01-13T00:22:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-13/nikkei-225-january-options-settle-at-8-470-71-traders-say.html
Japan ’s Nikkei 225 January options
settled at 8,470.71, traders said.  The Nikkei 225 Stock Average rose 1 percent to 8,464.86 as
of 9:09 a.m. in  Tokyo . The gauge closed at 8,385.59 yesterday.  The settlement price, also known as the “special
quotation,” of Nikkei 225 options is calculated after all
stocks in the Nikkei begin trading.  To contact the reporter for this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
